sequenceDiagram
    actor H as Human
    participant GD as /grill-with-docs
    participant WP as /write-prd
    participant TP as /testplan
    participant KB as Knowledge Base
    participant FS as docs/

    H->>GD: /grill-with-docs

    note over GD: Domain awareness (AFK)
    GD->>FS: Read CONTEXT.md / CONTEXT-MAP.md
    GD->>FS: Read docs/adr/ (existing decisions)
    GD->>KB: Read relevant system overviews + known-issues
    GD->>FS: Explore codebase patterns

    note over GD: Grill loop (one question at a time)
    loop Each design decision
        GD->>H: Question + recommended answer
        H->>GD: Answer
        alt Term conflicts with CONTEXT.md
            GD->>H: ⚠️ Glossary conflict — clarify
            H->>GD: Resolution
            GD->>FS: Update CONTEXT.md inline (immediately)
        end
        alt Decision is hard to reverse + surprising + has trade-offs
            GD->>FS: Write docs/adr/NNNN-[slug].md
        end
    end

    GD->>H: Shared Understanding Summary (decisions + CONTEXT.md updates + ADRs)
    H->>GD: Confirm → suggest /write-prd

    H->>WP: /write-prd

    note over WP: Phase 1 — AFK Explore
    WP->>FS: Read CONTEXT.md, DEVLOG.md, research/, prototype/
    WP->>FS: Explore codebase (modules, layers, existing patterns)
    WP->>WP: Identify modules (UI/DATA/LOGIC/SYNC/INFRA)
    WP->>H: Phase 1 Summary (modules, scope boundary, open questions)
    H->>WP: Confirm (or corrections)

    note over WP: Phase 2 — Write
    WP->>H: Module estimates (token cost band + story points per module)
    H->>WP: Confirm estimates
    alt XL module flagged
        WP->>H: ⚠️ XL — requires /break-down before /build
    end
    WP->>FS: Save docs/prd/active/[feature].md
    WP->>FS: Add kanban tickets to docs/kanban.md
    WP->>FS: Update idea diagram → diagram-v3-prd.mmd

    H->>TP: /testplan
    TP->>FS: Read PRD (user stories + DoD)
    TP->>FS: Read CONTEXT.md (domain language for test names)
    TP->>KB: Read relevant known-issues
    TP->>H: Draft testplan (automated + manual + not tested + critical path)
    H->>TP: Confirm
    TP->>FS: Assign TC-NNN IDs per test case
    TP->>FS: Update docs/tests/registry.md
    TP->>FS: Save docs/testplan-[feature].md
